        "cordex.atmos.key_properties.tuning_applied.description": {
            "values": [
                "The starting set-up was identical to that of the CORDEX-CORE. 5 year simulations [1999-2005] were run to test the configuration and compare to the EOBS (using seasonal biases, and PDFs). The simulations were repeated by changing cloud, convection, and other parameters (one at a time) in order to minimize the bias. The final configuration used was the best configuration obtained in the 6-month time-frame allocated for the tuning."
            ]
        }, 
